<paragraph blockId="17.[138,828,839,863]" box="[138,828,839,863]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2735">Twenty-one specimens were collected from Mount Taibai.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="17.[138,233,918,942]" box="[138,233,918,942]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2735">
